'''Protective Liquid Coating''' was a liquid used in the construction of [[Mandalorian armor/Legends|Mandalorian armor]]. When used on a substance, the Coating increased its damage resistance by protecting emulsions from abrasions and [[Water/Legends|water]] damage.

